# ============================================
  # Environment Variables for Generated Sites
  # ============================================
  #
  # These values are provided at RUNTIME, not in this file:
  #
  # VM Deployment:
  #   - Shared secrets come from /opt/shared/env/.env (symlinked)
  #   - Site-specific config comes from .env.local
  #
  # Cloud Run Deployment:
  #   - All secrets injected from Google Secret Manager
  #   - Public config passed as environment variables
  #
  # ============================================
  # Available Shared Secrets (same for all sites):
  # ============================================
  # 
  # Firebase (SHARED project):
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APP_ID
  #   GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS
  #
  # AWS SES (Email):
  #   AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID
  #   AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
  #   AWS_REGION
  #   AWS_SES_FROM_EMAIL
  #
  # Google Cloud Storage:
  #   GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT_ID
  #   GOOGLE_CLOUD_STORAGE_BUCKET
  #
  # AI APIs (VM only):
  #   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
  #   GEMINI_API_KEY
  #
  # ============================================
  # Site-Specific Variables (set at deployment):
  # ============================================
  #
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_ID - Your unique site ID
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUBDOMAIN_URL - Your site URL
  #   NEXT_PUBLIC_EDIT_MODE - true (VM) or false (Cloud Run)
  #
  # ============================================
